      <akn:section eId="sec_32_1455">
        <akn:num>32-1455</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Enforcement.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-1455_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>If an employer fails to comply with the provisions of this chapter, the Mayor shall assess a civil fine of $1,000 for the first violation, $5,000 for the second violation, and $20,000 for each subsequent violation.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-1455_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Adjudication for a violation of this chapter shall be pursuant to Chapter 18 of Title 2 [ยง 2-1801.01 et seq.].</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-1455_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Nothing in this chapter shall be construed to create a private right of action.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
